":"Your slaves","i":"عِبَادَكَ"},{"b":"5.3","h":"8.42","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"and not","i":"وَلَا"},{"b":"5.8","h":"9.44","c":"يَلِدُوٓاْ","d":"yalidū","e":"they will beget","i":"يَلِدُوۡۤا"},{"b":"7.9","h":"11.66","c":"إِلَّا","d":"illā","e":"except","i":"اِلَّا"},{"b":"8.7","h":"12.9","c":"فَاجِرٗا","d":"fājiran","e":"a wicked","i":"فَاجِرًا"},{"b":"10.4","h":"15","c":"كَفَّارٗا","d":"kaffāran","e":"a disbeliever","i":"كَفَّارًا"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, if You leave them, they will mislead Your servants and not beget except [every] wicked one and [confirmed] disbeliever."}},"28":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.15","c":"رَّبِّ","d":"rabbi","e":"My Lord!","i":"رَبِّ"},{"b":"0.6","h":"0.98","c":"ٱغۡفِرۡ","d":"igh'fir","e":"Forgive","i":"اغۡفِرۡ"},{"b":"1.0","h":"1.71","c":"لِي","d":"lī","e":"me","i":"لِىۡ"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.56","c":"وَلِوَٰلِدَيَّ","d":"waliwālidayya","e":"and my parents","i":"وَلِـوَالِدَىَّ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"5.13","c":"وَلِمَن","d":"waliman","e":"and whoever","i":"وَلِمَنۡ"},{"b":"4.7","h":"6.74","c":"دَخَلَ","d":"dakhala","e":"enters","i":"دَخَلَ"},{"b":"5.3","h":"7.74","c":"بَيۡتِيَ","d":"baytiya","e":"my house","i":"بَيۡتِىَ"},{"b":"6.1","h":"8.97","c":"مُؤۡمِنٗا","d":"mu'minan","e":"a believer","i":"مُؤۡمِنًا"},{"b":"6.8","h":"10.24","c":"وَلِلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ","d":"walil'mu'minīna","e":"and believing men","i":"وَّلِلۡمُؤۡمِنِيۡنَ"},{"b":"9.2","h":"13.53","c":"وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتِۖ","d":"wal-mu'mināti","e":"and believing women","i":"وَالۡمُؤۡمِنٰتِؕ"},{"b":"10.8","h":"15.97","c":"وَلَا","d":"walā","e":"And (do) not","i":"وَلَا"},{"b":"11.4","h":"16.92","c":"تَزِدِ","d":"tazidi","e":"increase","i":"تَزِدِ"},{"b":"12.0","h":"17.85","c":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","d":"l-ẓālimīna","e":"the wrongdoers","i":"الظّٰلِمِيۡنَ"},{"b":"13.6","h":"20.19","c":"إِلَّا","d":"illā","e":"except","i":"اِلَّا"},{"b":"14.5","h":"21.41","c":"تَبَارَۢا","d":"tabāran","e":"(in) destruction","i":"تَبَارًا"}],"a":{"g":"My Lord, forgive me and my parents and whoever enters my house a believer